Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新人闖了點禍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下
